center
tikzpicture[scale=0.7]
 (times) at (0,0) {$\times$};
 (plus) at (-1,-1) {$+$};
 (5) at (1,-1) {5};
 (3) at (-1.5,-2) {3};
 (4) at (-0.5,-2) {4};
 (times) – (plus);
 (times) – (5);
 (plus) – (3);
 (plus) – (4);
tikzpicture
center

Preorder: $\times + 3\, 4\, 5$ (prefix notation)

Inorder: $3 + 4 \times 5$ (needs parentheses!)

Postorder: $3\, 4 + 5 \times$ (postfix/RPN)
